---
const year = 2026;
const brand = "Moxie";
const supportEmail = "support@eigoonline.com";
---

<footer class="mt-14 border-t border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="/eigoonline_logo.png" alt="eigoonline.com" width="140" height="48" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="h-10 w-auto" />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600">
          オンライン英会話を目的別（総合/日常/ビジネス）に比較し、料金・特徴・無料体験・公式サイト導線までまとめてチェックできます。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-sm font-extrabold text-zinc-900">サイト</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700">
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/">TOP</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/ranking/list">ランキング</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/search">検索</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/article/list">コラム</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-sm font-extrabold text-zinc-900">お問い合わせ</div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-700">
          <a class="font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:underline" href={`mailto:${supportEmail}`}>{supportEmail}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 text-sm font-extrabold text-zinc-900">情報</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700">
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/info/company">運営者情報</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/info/policy">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/info/survey">調査・算定方法</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:underline" href="/inquiry/contact">掲載のお問い合わせ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-6 text-xs text-zinc-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <div>© {year} {brand}</div>
      <div class="text-zinc-500">All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

